{"id": 1171, "genre": 1000, "title": "为了显得不娘，男性如何艰难度过夏季？", "description": "就，看见树荫假装不经意地躲一躲或者包里常备藿香正气水掏出来喝。（题图来自：Steve Scott）", "record_count": 5264, "comment_count": 61, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160817220953UriSvu5aC2HzPqD8.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2016-08-17T17:00:05Z", "questions": [{"id": 1056, "title": "为了显得不娘，男性如何艰难度过夏季？", "content": "为了显得不娘，男性如何艰难度过夏季？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 107941, "content": "很少主动打遮阳伞，除非帮女朋友打的时候蹭一下", "image": "img/option/option/20160815214934o9nXPG6LS8iNamg7.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 107942, "content": "很少有正式的短裤，主打清凉的裤子长度依然过膝", "image": "img/option/option/20160815214948GBhFcp0tTmkXsAn5.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 107943, "content": "即使晒破皮，还是觉得涂防晒是女孩子做的事", "image": "img/option/option/20160815215842awNQp1BPFxMV0JOm.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 107944, "content": "不敢戴遮阳帽/墨镜，因为并不想引起注意", "image": "img/option/option/201608152146490QRlMtWwXkgvVNEn.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 107945, "content": "凉的衣服只有背心，胖瘦皆不宜穿", "image": "img/option/option/20160815215951oh61tiIxba0K5JSw.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 107946, "content": "不敢穿凉鞋上班", "image": "img/option/option/20160815215824iUZ0lL5KzMnAQbEu.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 107947, "content": "明明很喜欢草莓甜筒也只买运动饮料", "image": "img/option/option/20160815215030DxdnYgzRtGk1H72M.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 107948, "content": "无奈，只能靠走路带风来降温", "image": "img/option/option/20160815215802MmJ7cLi30AlxE6ny.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}